com.siperian.bdd.userexits.datamodel

Interface ChangedBDDObject


  • public interface ChangedBDDObject
    Contains list of changed children or grandchildren objects and their parent object. Each instance of this class is associated with a child or grandchild definition in BDD Configuration. All objects defined in Subject Area (primary object and all children) are represented by BDDObject class. This class is designed to contain list of changed children or grandchildren BDDObject and their parent BDDObject

    Operations and parameters in this interface assume that the user exit implementer uses the BDD configuraiton definitions to view the data structure, so names of operations and attributes corresponds to BDD application attributes.

    • Method Summary

      All Methods Instance Methods Abstract Methods

      Returns list of changed children or grandchildren objects.
